Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个和尚说的河边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…发带？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:03:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 你真的还活着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇的声音与桔梗的唇瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了 我的死期也就是你的死期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是抱着对你的怨恨死去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂永远停滞在那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你活在这个世上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就无法得到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了吗？桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像…很悲伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿过了我的结界吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结…结界？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么个东西吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集那些少女亡魂的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那样的话 请你让她们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉他…说要来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 犬夜叉正想到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是犬夜叉的什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体…动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…绊脚石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集亡魂的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有结界…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗就在这里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 真的是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我动不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是来救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是来见我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你捣乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捣乱？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你还是想杀了犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你误会了 桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有人故意让你们相互怨恨的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死你的根本不是犬夜叉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的表情好像在说我应该高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致我于死地的真凶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人死了 我就能复活吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死者的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是重新得到生命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 死者也有能够实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把那个最不该把我忘记的人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最不该把你忘记的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指犬夜叉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在期待我的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来他对我们的战斗还留有悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他去后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会让他忘了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也绝不会让时间前进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能在静止的时间里获得生命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能永远活在那家伙的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在犬夜叉也总是想着你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样还不够吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉是喜欢着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都在他心里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样还不够吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是带着对彼此的怨恨离别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的那种温暖的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会增加我们的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比让两个人的心结合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更能增加怨恨这种感情的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他爱我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就爱我的怨念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我 则深陷其中 去爱着他的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 你太不讲理了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样实在太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你快告诉桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉她你们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为被奈落骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉看不到我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你在收集少女的亡魂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个泥土和骨灰造就的虚假身躯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不填满灵魂就无法行动自如
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你很厌恶我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我靠着对你的怨恨支撑自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集死者的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而继续待在这世上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别…别胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你在怨恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没有忘记过你！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…犬夜叉一直对桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像…有点寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉被抢走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是跟犬夜叉在交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你变成什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不会觉得厌恶或憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我现在却有可能亲手杀了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 自从遇到你以后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不再是个巫女了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了一个普通的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我活着的时候就一直想像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…一下就接受了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 他当然会很自然地接受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我离他们这么近干嘛呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像个傻瓜一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 害我都哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊 我太没用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人怀念的桔梗的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟以前一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同的是已经不再温暖了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已然死去的身体如此冰冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此悲伤…如此寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经无法回到那个时侯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我想再这样待一会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本无法拯救桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果无法为她做任何事 干脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆就这样让时间静止…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…想让时间静止吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我什么都不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要跟…桔梗在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我快看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会妨碍你们的啦 快放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会自动消失的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们两个听到没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 我不会再让你走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起下地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他渐渐被拉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你在做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不快点逃走！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 他已经被夺去意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 你可以听到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说犬夜叉想跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是他没有说要陪你去死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉跟你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要打倒50年前设计陷害你们的奈落啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉最希望做的是活着战斗下去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为犬夜叉是想为你报仇啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他能复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这副身躯也不会再复活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其带着对我的思念活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如跟我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你所希冀的 是一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是因为犬夜叉失去了意识
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才不会跟你一起走呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我离犬夜叉远点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不准你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:12:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰犬夜叉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人…又要夺走我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在亡魂全部脱离这副身躯之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 犬夜叉 快点醒过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 犬夜叉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 快点醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 犬夜叉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…她在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这种地方干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你又在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人…比我还重要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 桔梗 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与你亲吻的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是虚假的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能一个人去找四魂之玉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能…没办法跟你一起去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:16:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你能看到四魂碎片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人肯定不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为那样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之所以需要我 只是因为那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像在说废话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 就当你刚才什么都没听到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能因为我孤独一人待在陌生的世界吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得有点寂寞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…有我在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能陪着你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看不见我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从头到尾都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…你让我一个人待会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部是什么啊…全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…那时候我做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:16:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 戈薇 告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说全部就是全部啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都在特等席看得清清楚楚的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？找到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这个地方干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你有没有看到戈薇？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个倒下的姿势好眼熟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来戈薇小姐没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说戈薇现在精神的不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？阿枫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕我这个姐姐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:18:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我听说姐姐您从悬崖顶上摔了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为您已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我已经是死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我还对这世间充满了迷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还想要犬夜叉的性命吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我跟犬夜叉见过面了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没能取他性命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我 阿枫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你所知道的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于奈落的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我这腐坏的灵魂也不是一无是处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很好吃吧？很想吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要一个能自由行动的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了夺取四魂之玉 并让桔梗成为我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:18:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 吃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后给我身体 给我力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都起源于鬼蜘蛛的邪念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把身体交给聚集而来的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 妖怪奈落就诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 原来是那个山贼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还说四魂之玉被玷污后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会更加美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我和犬夜叉可悲地互相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了得到被污染的玉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉也中了奈落的圈套 受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道自己的死因罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 犬夜叉变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的表情变得温柔多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:20:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去他总是带着不相信任何人的执拗的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇是个不可思议的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在一点点地治愈犬夜叉的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是那个女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她改变了犬夜叉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该由我来治愈犬夜叉的心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是无法放弃对世间的迷恋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您要在这世间徘徊到何时…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她回去了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得戈薇小姐那个样子很不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟桔梗小姐到底发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你总是跟女人做的那些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然在戈薇小姐面前做出那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你平时到底在做什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇还会不会回来呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像下了很大的决心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没有忘记过你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那句话…是发自内心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与你亲吻的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:21:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是虚假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她对我也是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人…比我重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.00,0:22:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 现在怎么办？犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗小姐应该还没走远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.34,0:22:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要追她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 戈薇比较重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 快点去跟戈薇和好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一时都昏了头 连行李都忘了带了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那上面有人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.73,0:22:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么办？犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要选谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.97,0:22:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个都选行不行啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想脚踏两条船？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为男人我能了解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 就算撕裂你的嘴 都不能让她们本人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一被发现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:22:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.72,0:23:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 你就得坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就叫做天谴对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我觉得犬夜叉也没有什么恶意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}我们在生命的旅程中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.80,0:23:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}逐渐失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}仍坚信并追逐着光明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.77,0:23:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}现在与你一同启航
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}在那深深的丛林中 即使是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}也一定埋藏着被抛弃的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}若能操控时光的轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.67,0:24:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}或许可以再次翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.32,0:24:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}我们一边迷茫彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.12,0:24:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}生存下去 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.22,0:24:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}仍坚信并追逐着光明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}现在与你一同启航
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.29,0:24:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说附近有个除妖师的村庄
